ENSTAR GROUP LIMITED, Starstone US Holdings Inc., Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Gareth NOKES, Defendant-Movant. M-1183 September Term 2017
080949 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 21, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to appeal is granted and the matter is summarily remanded to the Superior Court, Appellate Division to consider on the merits.
